{"tid":1769534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"國家憲法日 | 葉國謙:外國勢力插手香港事務 23條立法有實際需要","createTime":"2019-12-05T02:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T19:11:27.000Z","uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d8beefb939981a68fa31b65e8f3001c90748d7c9","tid":1769534,"uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVFJA6G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVFJA6G.jpg&h=a118ad7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【文匯網訊】大公文匯全媒體報道：港區全國人大代表、行政會議成員葉國謙今日(4日)出席2019「國家憲法日」座談會後，談到23條立法問題。他表示，香港已經回歸22年，近期事件可看到外國勢力不斷干擾及插手香港事務，這已經危害到香港社會以及國家安全，所以基本法23條立法是有實際需要。<br />\n葉國謙強調，23條立法是市民的公民責任，能否實行需要各方面的條件同環境，他希望特區政府能認真積極考慮立法，並有序地進行，向市民解釋立法的需要，而非「坐係到等運到」。<br />\n他又提到，近日美國通過涉港法案，所提到的香港民主人權現況不是基於事實，有份促成法案的香港人士則要為自己的所作所為受到譴責。"},{"pid":"f83a82e734ff104e77c0bdd575ed0bc3ef6f63a1","tid":1769534,"uid":7609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:51:59.000Z","msg":"立你老母個老母"},{"pid":"0f90c8da1011c14c91a2e572fba104ff6909e9a4","tid":1769534,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T02:54:47.000Z","msg":"英國美國加拿大都攻擊緊中國<br />\n但啲tweets無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Rt + like + reply</span></span><br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=nBH2CsHB%2BCaOzcOtxJw1e6joMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=55a36d77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task2</span></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"ed7a61218fadcba607335f348260d7be654a126f","tid":1769534,"uid":243769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T03:08:04.000Z","msg":"呢個就死嘅垃圾人  有咩資格響度說三道四"},{"pid":"9031cfc8dcbf29ddee1b64ae3be2d459030973a8","tid":1769534,"uid":52192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T19:07:45.000Z","msg":"強烈譴責呢條賣港支拿畜生對香港問題說三道四<br />\n要求立法合法人道毀滅呢類賣港畜生"},{"pid":"2abb9df51da27d4f19abd87d47eccacba61f3339","tid":1769534,"uid":141097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T19:11:27.000Z","msg":"試咗制裁先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}